@Node    envList  Listview Gadget

   @{u}List of environment names@{uu}

    This Gadget shows a List of environments in your system. User the Arrow
    or slider Gadgets to scroll up and down. You can also user your Keyboard
    to scroll. Keys are:

    Arrow up        to scroll up
    Arrow down        to scroll down

    numeric Keypad "8"    to scroll up
    numeric Keypad "2"    to scroll down
    numeric Keypad "7"    to scroll top of list
    numeric Keypad "1"    to scroll end of list
    numeric Keypad "9"    to scroll one page up
    numeric Keypad "3"    to scroll one page down

    The selected name of a environment is shown in the @{"sting gadget" link envlistst} underneath.
    On Kickstart 3.0 and newer the selected name is also shown with a inverted
    barrel on the listview gadget. double Click on one name force a pop-up
    the  @{"Getenv requester" link envget}.

@endnode
@Node   envlistst "environment/String"

    @{u}Name string gadget@{uu}

    This gadget shows the name of the selected environment. You can select a env-
    ironment by one click on listview gadget.

    If you click on string gadget you can enter Charaters from your Keyboard.
    When finished press <RETURN> or <ENTER>, if this environment already exists
    the program force the @{"Getenv requester" link envget}, if not the @{"AddNew requester" link envadd}.

@endnode
